                Bon<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> m<expan><ex>em</ex><abbr>o</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="2"/>ri<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> Ianac<lb break="no" n="3"/>is bixit <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>n</ex></expan><lb break="no" n="4"/>os III bon<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="5"/>memori<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="6"/>Iobris bi<lb break="no" n="7"/>xit <note>sic</note> in pac<lb break="no" n="8"/>e an<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>os</abbr></expan> VI <lb n="9"/>plus mi<lb break="no" n="10"/>nus
